      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eatonville%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The town hosts the annual Zora Neale Hurston Festival, celebrating the author’s legacy and African American arts since 1990.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
